lead_paragraph: Germany's record goalscorer Miroslav Klose is starting a traineeship with the national team as the retired striker looks to kick off his coaching career, the German Football Association said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: World Cup Winner Klose Starts Germany Traineeship
